private void  (HttpServletRequest req){ String expectedUser=req.getHeader("ExpectedUser"); if (expectedUser == null) { throw new IllegalStateException("No ExpectedUser received."); } if (expectedUser.equals("None")) { if (req.getRemoteUser() != null) { throw new IllegalStateException("Unexpected RemoteUser returned."); } if (req.getUserPrincipal() != null) { throw new IllegalStateException("Unexpected UserPrincipal returned."); } } else { if (req.getRemoteUser().equals(expectedUser) == false) { throw new IllegalStateException("Different RemoteUser returned."); } if (req.getUserPrincipal().getName().equals(expectedUser) == false) { throw new IllegalStateException("Different UserPrincipal returned."); } } }
